{"tid":2383852,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"72歲退休婦健身中心遇上27歲教練　被呃350萬元財物","createTime":"2021-01-28T07:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T23:12:17.000Z","uid":20933,"like":10,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e3cfe69f246feb9e57820a108c1d1134fef17dd4","tid":2383852,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T07:38:30.000Z","msg":"秀茂坪警區刑事調查隊督察譚樂恩表示，事件發生在2012年，老婦在連鎖健身中心購買了為期15年的健身會籍及課程，總值200萬元，但其後她因為個人原因想要退會，被捕健身教練於是利用老婦想要取回金錢的心理，聲稱可替她取回所有會費，從中欺騙對方金錢。<br />\n<br />\n譚樂恩稱，老婦只是一名普通退休人士，並非城中名媛，當年以健康理由參加健身課程，其間在課堂上認識該名健身教練。當健身教練得知老婦想要退會取回會費時，於是當面向老婦進行游說，在博取到對方信任後，再向對方提出可替她取回會費的建議，但要收取金錢及4隻合共90萬元的名錶作為手續費，老婦信以為真，結果墮入騙局，損失合共350萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210128/SZPXJTCIYJA3DOM4OQS2XJD5HQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210128%2FSZPXJTCIYJA3DOM4OQS2XJD5HQ%2F&d=LvSu6Mc%2FVB7R449T953cU6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=8acd174a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210128%2FSZPXJTCIYJA3DOM4OQS2XJD5HQ%2F&h=955e1916\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210128/SZPXJTCIYJA3DOM4OQS2XJD5HQ/</a>"},{"pid":"e22f3676a0577cdc9ed3863b6f01ab709e360656","tid":2383852,"uid":132810,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T07:39:14.000Z","msg":"教練比我呃上床，就試過"},{"pid":"f082628b67831efb8c6acb7d78e8337f33399377","tid":2383852,"uid":6696,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T07:46:08.000Z","msg":"70歲仲健身<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e3d9db7791f9ba9e2c35fac5e0cfe3b5abd4e3","tid":2383852,"uid":31962,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T07:53:27.000Z","msg":"72歲買15年健身會藉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鬥長命"},{"pid":"0a89938633907cab0855f0d6b647706197450e82","tid":2383852,"uid":378793,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy"